{"tid":2312963,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【無圖】人生第一次3p...（長文慎入）","createTime":"2020-12-05T11:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T13:03:09.000Z","uid":314908,"like":12,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e010637740c72519363ded1806c6af829e590489","tid":2312963,"uid":314908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T11:58:56.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我識左十幾年既老死話識左條SP，好撚正，好撚索，把聲仲好溫柔，我心諗關我咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢就話，條女想試下3p，我腎上腺素即刻上升，係到諗係咪叫埋我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我個fd就問下我想唔想試下，dry再咁多年既我就即刻應承：「um...都得既。」「有無相先？」然後佢就話返到屋企sd比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哇屌！正撚到 完全係魔鬼身材 個樣又後生 完全無半點大陸雞既味道 最重要既係聽日就可以試下佢手勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到第二日，飛機都無打，特登儲定然後留比條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我個晚要ot 要夜啲先join到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我特登飛的去萬X酒店，上到酒店房門，已經隱約聽到啲jit jit聲同叫床聲，心諗個死仔唔等埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我敲門之後，入到去見到我個fd同條女都除晒衫，條女個身材真係好正，個波大到應該可以用黎幫我打飛機，對腳又白又滑，保養得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然望到我個fd條jer有啲尷尬，但係有女屌就無所謂啦。<br />\n<br />\n「快啲除褲啦。」條女把聲真係好溫柔，我即刻急不及待，除晒衫褲鞋襪，準備進入戰鬥狀態。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始，條女一到含我，一到比我個fd插，個樣真好淫，口技又好，含到咁上下，我拍一拍我個fd個膊頭話「不如調轉？」我個fd含春咁既樣對住我笑，心諗洗唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n當我想企係個陣，我個fd突然捉住我，將我壓左係佢下面，心諗pk了，調轉唔係調轉比你屌喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但係我比較矮，又細力，我個fd就尖撚黎，佢一野lur左啖口水落手到，然後搽落我屎眼到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，摩都無摩到就插左入黎，哇 我屌，估唔到又幾撚爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我個身唔覺意咁郁左下，佢就頂得更加大力 頂得更加深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我一直都係到嗌「唔好，好痛」但係佢無理到我，仲越插越大力，插左十幾分鐘，佢無端端震左一下，然後我feel到個屎眼暖暖地，shit，唔係射撚左下嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後佢趴左係我身到，然後講左句「好爽，估唔到你都鍾意玩後面。」 我個樣即刻變成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都無講過我鍾意，但係又真係幾舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後勸大家一句，無咩都唔好玩3p，唔係既話，會中途轉機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb00f5ec5383e4fd585511dbb1c7bb5cf9f22cdf","tid":2312963,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T12:01:27.000Z","msg":"有用po推"},{"pid":"09a97ff5841b9d8e211ba60c501d2fd70d3247bb","tid":2312963,"uid":208180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T12:02:07.000Z","msg":"我入到嚟"},{"pid":"d7e078656154fb684c59b170ff9f8473fa80f4af","tid":2312963,"uid":314908,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"09a97ff5841b9d8e211ba60c501d2fd70d3247bb","tid":2312963,"uid":208180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T12:02:07.000Z","msg":"我入到嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T12:02:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9adf7bdee0e001c0fbc4639babc5c66d58f543","tid":2312963,"uid":370289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T12:03:08.000Z","msg":"把聲好溫柔？"},{"pid":"63881bcec31c7d8eb33eb1faeeaed53dad90d9fb","tid":2312963,"uid":343134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T12:04:38.000Z","msg":"樓主天生淫0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ac043c05cea975ddbddc9a212126651f43658f9","tid":2312963,"uid":314908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63881bcec31c7d8eb33eb1faeeaed53dad90d9fb","tid":2312963,"uid":343134,"